{"tid":1982772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★油價暴瀉至「負數」 市場沽其他資產填數","createTime":"2020-04-21T11:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T13:37:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61823e8640c994ee0da6aa394d61bfeb2281c744","tid":1982772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"油價暴瀉至「負數」，市場人士估計，當中不少大型機構投資者會因對沖油價而損失慘重，料會沽售其他資產填數，尤其是金價有不俗升值。目前現貨金剛剛跌穿每安士1,670美元，最新報1,669.95美元，跌1.52%。<br />\n<br />\n獨立外匯商品分析師盧楚仁預計，油市爆煲會觸發比2008年金融海嘯更糟的環球金融危機，投資者要勒緊安全帶。<br />\n<br />\n他指，是次油價大跌至負數屬史無前例，令很多投資者跌眼鏡。而此爆跌是因5月份紐約原油期貨於美國時間周二(21日)到期，好友慌忙斬倉及轉倉所引發。<br />\n<br />\n他忠告，投資者不能輕視是次斬倉及轉倉潮的後遺症。其牽連甚廣，因不少機構投資者，例如銀行、油公司、航空公司、基金公司或投行等都會買期油對沖油價上漲風險，所以估計他們在是次油價爆跌中慘蝕，並會於未來3個月陸續披露虧損。而這批機構投資者面對資金周轉不靈，好可能會在其他資產中套現，令多個資產類別都出現骨牌效應而暴瀉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200421/bkn-20200421193145898-0421_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200421%2Fbkn-20200421193145898-0421_00842_001.html&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=8d07af1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200421/bkn-20200421193145898-0421_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7662db154ed258dc9fdbbcae1d9f0de2e44a8185","tid":1982772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaa3955edb20bc3c35e4ec91ef43d92551a23be","tid":1982772,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"price in 咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264a62163f667009e7c36e09bcd40f69f168e706","tid":1982772,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e30e6ed7a08c927ead47df6fc7f4ecedbed055","tid":1982772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"沽港樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升到咁高 why not"},{"pid":"33506fecb37613ab808882f77dd7a92599dcfdc3","tid":1982772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}